hadiths[184]{hadithnumber,text}:
1772,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ko Yamen bheja to farmaya : ''tum ehle-kitab ke paas ja rahey ho, unhen is gawahi deney ki taraf dawat dena ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin aur be-shak Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah ke Rasool hain, agar wo is mein tumhari itaat kar lein to unhen bataao ke Allah ne din raat mein un par paanch namazein farz ki hain, agar wo is mein bhi tumhari itaat karen to unhen batana ke Allah ne un par sadqa farz kiya hai, jo unke maal daaron se lekar unke naadaaron (ghareebon) ko diya jaeyga, agar wo tumhari ye baat bhi maan lein to phir unke achhey achhey maal leney se bachna, aur mazloom ki badduaa se bachna kyonkey uskey aur Allah ke darmiyan koi hijaab nahin.'' muttafaq aleh."
1773,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo soney chaandi ka Malik uska haq ada nahin karta to jab qiyamat ka din hoga to uskey liye aag ki takhtiyan banai jaeyngi aur unhen jahannam ki aag mein tapaya jaeyga, aur phir unke sath uskey pehlu , uski peshani aur uski pusht ko daaghaa jaeyga, jab wo takhtiyan thandi ho jaeyngi to unhen garm karney ke liye dobara jahannam mein lotaya jaeyga . aur ye amal us roz musalsal jari rahega jiski miqdaar pachas hazar saal hogi , yahan tak ke bandon ke darmiyan faisla kar diya jaeyga, pas wo apna raasta, jannat ya jahannam ki taraf dekh lega .'' arz kya gaya, Allah ke Rasool ! to oont ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' oonton ka jo Malik unki Zakat ada nahin karta , aur unka eik haq ye bhi hai ke pani pilaney ki baari waley din unka doodh (pani ke ghaat par mojud zarurat mandon ke liye ( dohaa jaey, (aur wo ye bhi na karey ( to jab qiyamat ka din hoga to us shakhs ko eik chatiyal maidan mein un oonton ke samney chehrey ya pusht ke bal gira diya jaeyga, aur ye oont pehley se ziyada motey tazey hongey, wo un mein se eik bachey ko bhi gum nahin paeyga, wo apney khuron se usey ronden gey aur apney munhon se usey kaatengey, jab unka pehla oont guzar jaeyga to is par unka aakhiri oont phir lota diya jaeyga, aur ye silsila us din, jiski miqdaar pachas hazar saal hogi, jari rahega yahan tak ke bandon ke darmiyan faisla kar diya jaeyga, pas wo apni raah dekh lega, jannat ki taraf ya jahannam ki taraf.'' arz kya gaya, Allah ke Rasool ! to gaey aur bakri ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' gaey aur bakriyon ka jo Malik unka haq (yani Zakat) ada nahin karta, to jab qiyamat ka din hoga to usey eik chatiyal maidan mein chehrey ke bal gira diya jaeyga, wo un mein se kisi eik ko bhi gum nahin paeyga, aur un mein se koi mudey huey seengon wali hogi na seeng ke baghair aur na hi kisi ke seeng tootey huey hongey, ye apney seengon se usey maarengi aur apney khuron se usey rondengi. jab un mein se pehli is par guzar jaeygi to unki aakhiri phir is par lota di jaeygi, aur ye silsila us din , jiski miqdaar pachas hazar saal hogi , chalta rahega yahan tak ke bandon ke darmiyan faisla kar diya jaeyga, wo apna raasta , jannat ki taraf ya jahannam ki taraf dekh lega .'' aap se arz kya gaya, Allah ke Rasool! to ghodey? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ghodey teen qism ke hain : eik wo jo aadmi ke liye bojh hain, eik wo jo aadmi ke liye parda hain aur eik wo jo aadmi ke liye baaise-ajr hain, raha wo jo uskey liye gunah hai, wo aadmi jisney riya, fakhr aur ehle-Islam ki dushmani ki khatir usey baandha to is qism ka ghoda us shakhs ke liye gunah hai, raha wo jo uskey liye parda hai, ye wo jisey koi aadmi Allah ki raah mein (nek-niyati ke sath) baandhey, phir wo unki pushton aur unki gardanon ke barey mein Allah ka haq na bhooley to ye uskey liye parda ( safed poshi ka baais) hain, aur raha wo ghoda, jo us shakhs ke liye baaise-ajr hai, to ye wo hai jisey aadmi ne Allah ki raah mein jihad karney ke liye ehle-Islam ki khatir kisi chara-gaah ya kisi baagh mein baandha, ye ghoda us chara-gaah ya us baagh se jo kuch khayega to uski khai gaee chiz ki miqdaar ke barabar uskey liye nekiyan likhi jaeyngi, aur agar wo rassi tudwa kar eik ya do tilon par chadhta aur koodta hai aur wo us doran jitney qadam chalta hai aur jis qadr leed karta hai to unki tadaad ke mutabiq us shakhs ke liye nekiyan likhi jati hain, aur agar uska Malik usey kisi nehar se lekar guzrey aur wo us se pani pi ley, halanke wo usey pani pilaana nahin chahta tha, to wo jis qadr pani piyega to Allah usi qadr uskey liye nekiyan likh lega.'' arz kya gaya, Allah ke Rasool! to gadhey? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''gadhon ke barey mein us naadir aur Jaame aayat ke ilawa mujh par aur kuch nazil nahin kya gaya : ''jo koi zarra barabar neki kerega to wo usey dekh lega aur jo koi zarra barabar burai kerega to wo usey dekh lega.'' rawahu Muslim."
1774,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah jis shakhs ko maal ata farmaai aur phir wo shakhs uski Zakat ada na karey to roze-qiyamat uskey maal ko ganjey azdaha ki surat mein bana diya jaeyga, uski aakhon par do nuqtey hongey, usko uskey galey ka haar bana diya jaeyga, phir wo usey jabdon se pakad kar kahega : main tera maal hun, main tera khazana hun, phir aapney ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''jo log bukhl kartey hain wo ye khayal na keren'' Bukhari."
1775,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ke paas oont ya gaey ya bakriyan hon aur wo unki Zakat ada na karta ho to unhen roze-qiyamat laya jaeyga to wo jis qadr (duniya mein) thin us se kahin badhi aur ziyada moti hongi, wo apney khuron se usey rondengi aur apney seengon ke sath usey maarengi, jab un mein se aakhiri guzar jaeygi to phir pehli ko dobara laya jaeyga, aur ye silsila jari rahega yahan tak ke logon ke darmiyan faisla kar diya jaeyga.'' muttafaq aleh."
1776,"Hazrat Jarir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab koi sadqa wasul karney wala tumharey paas aaye to jab wo tum se wapis jaey to usey tum se razi hona chahiye.'' rawahu Muslim ."
1777,"Hazrat Abdullah bin abi Aufi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab koi qom Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas sadqa lekar aati to aap dua farmatey : ''aey Allah! falan ki aal par rehmat farma.'' jab merey walid sadqa lekar aap ki khidmat mein hazir huey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! abu Aufi ki aal par rehmat farma .'' Bukhari, Muslim . eik riwayat mein hai : jab koi aadmi apna sadqa lekar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hota to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey : ''aey Allah ! is par rehmat farma .'' muttafaq aleh."
1778,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne umr ko sadqa wasul karney ke liye bheja to aap ko bataya gaya ke ibne-jameel (Raziallahu anhu), Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Zakat rok li hai, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ibne-jameel to is wajeh se inkar karta hai ke wo tang dast tha aur Allah aur uskey Rasool ne usey maal daar kar diya, raha Khalid, to tum Khalid par zulm kartey ho, usney to apni zirhen aur aalaate-jang Allah ki raah mein waqf kar rakhey hain, aur rahey Abbas to unki Zakat aur uskey barabar wo merey zimma hai.'' phir farmaya : '' umr ! kya aap ko malum nahin ke aadmi ka chacha uskey baap ki tarah hota hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1779,"Hazrat abu-Humaid Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Azd qabiley ke ibne-Lutbiya naami shakhs ko sadqaat wasul karney par maamoor farmaya, jab wo wapis aaya to usney kaha : ye (maal) tumharey liye hai aur ye mujhey hadiya (tohfa diya gaya hai) (ye sun kar) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khutba irshad farmaya to Allah ki hamd w sanaa bayan ki, phir farmaya : ''main tum mein se kuch aadmiyon ko un umur (baton) par , jo Allah ne merey supurd kiye hain, maamoor karta hun to un mein se koi aa kar kehta hai : ye ( maal ( tumharey liye hai aur ye hadiya hai jo mujhey diya gaya hai, wo apney walid ya apni walida ke ghar kyon na betha raha aur wo dekhta ke aaya usey hadiya ( tohfa ( milta hai ya nahin, us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! tum mein se jo shakhs is (maale-sadqaat) mein se jo kuch lega wo roze-qiyamat usey apni gardan par uthaey huey aaeyga, agar wo oont hua to wo aawaz kar raha hoga, agar gaey hui to wo aawaz kar rahi hogi, aur agar wo bakri hui to wo mimiya rahi hogi.'' phir aapney apney haath buland kiye yahan tak ke ham ne aap ki baghlon ki safedi dekhi, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah! kya maine pahuncha diya? aey Allah kya maine pahuncha diya?'' muttafaq aleh. Imam Khattabi ne farmaya : aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki riwayat ke alfaz : ''wo apni maa ya apney baap ke ghar kyon na betha raha, pas wo ye dekhta ke aaya usey hadiya (tohfa) milta hai ya nahin? ''main daleel hai ke her wo kaam jo kisi mana kiye gaey kaam ka wasila baney to wo bhi mamnoo hai, aur uqood mein dakhil honey wali her chiz dekhi jaeygi ke aaya jab wo chiz akeli ho to uska hukm isi tarah hoga jis tarah milaaney se hoga ya nahin, Sharahus-sunnah mein isi tarah hai."
1780,"Hazrat Adi bin Umaira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ham tum mein se jis shakhs ko kisi kaam par maamoor karen aur agar wo ham se eik sui ya us se bhi koi chhoti chiz chupa ley to ye khayanat hogi , jisey wo roze-qiyamat lekar hazir hoga .'' rawahu Muslim ."
1781,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab ye aayat : ''jo log sona chaandi zakhira kartey hain, '' nazil hui to ye musalmanon par bahut giraan guzri , to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : main tumhari is mushkil ko hal karta hun, wo gaey aur arz kya, Allah ke nabi! ye aayat aap ke Sahaba par bahut giraan guzri hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne Zakat isliye farz ki hai taake wo tumharey baqi amwaal ko paak kar dey, aur usney virasat ko isliye farz kya. ''raawi kehtey hain : aapney eik kalma zikr kya : ''taake wo tumharey baad walon ke liye ho jaey.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne (khushi ke sath) naara takbir buland kya, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen farmaya : ''kya main tumhen aadmi ke behtareen khazaney ke mutalliq na bataaun? wo nek biwi hai, jab wo uski taraf dekhey to wo usey khush kar dey, jab wo usey hukm dey to wo uski itaat karey aur jab wo uskey paas na ho to wo us (ke tamam huqooq) ki hifazat karey.''"
1782,"Hazrat Jabir bin Ateek (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' an-qareeb kuch Sawar (chhotey qafle ki surat mein) tumharey paas aaeyngey jinko tum na pasand karogey, agar wo tumharey paas ayen to unhen khush aamadeed kehna, aur (Zakat ki mad mein) jo wo chahen unhen leney dena, agar wo insaf karengey to apney faeede ke liye aur agar wo zulm karengey to wo unki jaan par hoga, aur unhen khush kar do, kyonkey tumhari Zakat ka itmaam unki razamandi hai, aur unhen tumharey haq mein dua kerni chahiye.''"
1783,"Hazrat Jarir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, kuch dehati Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to unhoney arz kya : sadqa wasul karney waley kuch log hamarey paas aatey hain to wo ham par zulm kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' apney sadqa wasul karney walon ko khush karo.'' unhoney arz kya. Allah ke Rasool ! chahey wo ham par zulm keren? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' apney sadqa wasul karney walon ko khush karo chahey tum par zulm kya jaey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
1784,"Hazrat Bashir bin Khasasiya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham ne arz kya : ke ehle sadqa ham par ziyadti kartey hain, kya ham unki ziyadti ke mutabiq apney amwaal mein se chupa liya keren? farmaya : ''nahin.''"
1785,"Hazrat Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haq w sadaaqat ke sath sadqaat wasul karney wala shakhs, Allah ki raah mein jihad karney waley shakhs ki tarah hai yahan tak ke wo (sadqa wasul karney wala) apney ghar wapis aa jaey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi ."
1786,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Zakat wasul karney wala Zakat se door beth kar maale-Zakat apney paas bulaey na Zakat deney waley apna maal apney gharon se door ley jaeyn aur sadqaat unke gharon mein wasul kiye jaeyn.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
1787,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi maal se istifaada karey to saal guzarney se pehley is par koi Zakat nahin hogi .'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney eik jamaat ka zikr kya ke unhoney usey ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) par moquf qarar diya hai."
1788,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se saal guzarney se pehley hi apni Zakat jald ada karney ke barey mein masla puchha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is barey mein unhen ijazat marahmat farmaai.
1789,"Hazrat umr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne logon ko khutba irshad farmatey huey farmaya : '' sun lo jo shakhs kisi yateem ka sarparast baney aur yateem ka kuch maal ho to wo us se tijarat karey aur usey aisey hi pada na rehney dey ke Zakat hi usey khatam kar dey .'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : iski sanad mein kalam hai, kyonkey Musanna bin Sabaah zaeef hain."
1790,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wafat pai aur unke baad abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) khalifa baney to kuch Arab murtad ho gaey, umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : aap logon se kaisey qitaal karengey jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farma chukey hain : ''mujhey logon se qitaal karney ka hukm diya gaya hai yahan tak ke wo kahin ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, jisney keh diya, Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin to usney haq Islam ke ilawa apney maal w jaan ko mujh se mehfooz kar liya , jabkey uska hisab Allah ke zimme hai.'' abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki qasam! jo shakhs Namaz aur Zakat mein farq kerega to main us se zarur qitaal karunga, kyonkey Zakat maal ka haq hai, Allah ki qism ! agar unhoney bhed ka bachcha, jo wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko diya kartey they, mujhey deney se inkar kya to main uskey inkar par bhi un se zarur qitaal karunga , umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Allah ki qism ! mujhey to bas yehi samajh aai ke Allah ne abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke seeney ko qitaal ke liye khol diya, maine pehchan liya ke wo haq par hain. muttafaq aleh."
1791,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se kisi eik ka khazana roze-qiyamat ganja azdaha bin jaeyga, us ( khazaney (ka Malik us se farar ikhtiyar kerega jabkey wo usey chodega nahin yahan tak ke wo uski ungliyon samet usey kha jaeyga.'' rawahu Ahmed ."
1792,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aapney farmaya : ''jo shakhs apney maal ki Zakat ada nahin karta to Allah roze-qiyamat usey uski gardan mein azdaha bana dega, phir aapney uskey misdaaq Allah azz-w-jall ki kitab se tilawat farmaai : ''jo log Allah ke ata kiye huey maal mein bukhl kartey hain, wo guman na keren'' aakhir tak . rawahu Tirmizi w Nasai w ibne-Maja ."
1793,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jis maal mein Zakat khalt-malt ho jaey to wo ( Zakat ( usko khatam kar deti hai.'' Shafai , Imam Bukhari ne usey apni taareekh mein riwayat kya hai, aur Imam Humaidi ne ye izafa naqal kya hai : agar tum par Zakat wajib ho aur phir tum usey ada na karo to is tarah haram, halal ko tabah kar dega, us se un logon ne daleel li hai jo samajhtey hain ke Zakat aen maal se ada karna farz hai. muntaqa mein bhi isi tarah hai. Behaqi ne Imam Ahmed bin Hanbal se apni sanad se Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) tak Shobil-emaan mein bayan kya hai aur Imam Ahmed ne '' Zakat ka maal milaaney.'' ki tafseer bayan kartey huey kaha is se murad ye hai ke koi maal daar shakhs Zakat wasul karey jabkey ye fuqaraa ka haq hai."
1794,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''paanch wasq se kam khajoor par, paanch auqiya se kam chaandi par aur paanch se kam oonton par Zakat nahin.'' muttafaq aleh."
1795,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' musalman par uskey ghulam aur uskey ghodey par Zakat nahin.'' aur eik riwayat mein hai : ''uskey ghulam par sadqa fitr ke siwa koi sadqa wajib nahin.'' muttafaq aleh."
1796,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhen Behrin ki taraf bheja to unhoney mujhey ye tehreer di : '' shuru Allah ke naam ke sath jo bahut meharban aur nihayat rehem karney wala hai, ye fariza Zakat jisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne musalmanon par farz qarar diya, jiskey mutalliq Allah ne apney Rasool ko hukm farmaya , jis musalman se us tareeqey par Zakat ka mutalba kya jaey to wo usey ada karey aur jis se us mashroo tareeqey se ziyada ka mutalba kya jaey to wo na dey . chobis aur us se kam oont par Zakat mein bakriyan li jaeyngi her paanch oont par eik bakri hai, jab oont pachchis se pentees ho jaeyn to phir un par oont ka eik saala muannas bacha bator Zakat liya jaeyga, jab oont chhattis se pentalis tak pahunch jaeyn to un par do baras ki oontni wajib hai, jab chhiyalis se saath tak pahunch jaeyn to un par teen baras mukammal honey ke baad chauthey saal wali oontni wajib hai jo gabhan honey ke qabil ho, jab iksath se pachhattar ho jaeyn to un par chaar baras mukammal honey ke baad paanchwen baras wali oontni wajib hai, jab wo 76 se nawwey ho jaeyn to un par do do saal ki do oontniyaan wajib hain, aur jab ikkyanwe se eik so bees ho jaeyn to phir un par teen baras mukammal karkey chauthey saal ki do oontniyaan wajib hain jo ke gabhan honey ke qabil hun, aur jab eik so bees se zayed ho jaeyn to phir her chaalis par do saala oontni aur her pachas par eik teen aur chaar saal ke darmiyan wali oontni wajib hai, aur jis shakhs ke paas sirf chaar oont hon to is par koi Zakat farz nahin hoti albatta agar unka Malik chahey ( to nafli sadqa kar sakta hai) jab paanch ho jaeyn to phir un par eik bakri wajib hai, aur jis shakhs par sadqa mein chaar aur paanch baras ke darmiyan ki oontni farz ho lekin uskey paas uskey bajaey teen aur chaar saal ke darmiyan ki oontni ho to us se ye qubul kar li jaeygi aur agar usey muyassar ho to wo uskey sath do bakriyan milaaeyga, ya phir bees dirham, aur jis shakhs par sadqa mein teen aur chaar saal ke darmiyan ki oontni farz ho lekin uskey paas iskey bajaey chaar aur paanch saal ke darmiyan ki oontni ho to us se ye wasul ki jaaeygi aur sadqa wasul karney wala usey bees dirham ya do bakriyan dega, aur jis shakhs par teen aur chaar saal ke darmiyan ki oontni farz hoti ho uskey paas ye na ho balke uskey paas do saal ki oontni ho to us se ye qubul kar li jaeygi aur wo uskey sath do bakriyan ya bees dirham ada kerega, aur jis shakhs par sadqa mein do saal ki oontni farz ho lekin uskey paas teen aur chaar saal ke darmiyan ki oontni ho to us se yehi qubul kar li jaeygi lekin sadqa wasul karney wala usey bees dirham ya do bakriyan dega , aur jis shakhs par sadqa mein do saal ki oontni farz ho lekin uskey paas ye na ho balke uskey paas eik saal ki oontni ho to us se yehi eik saal ki oontni qubul ki jaeygi aur wo uskey sath bees dirham ya do bakriyan ada kerega, aur isi tarah jis shakhs par sadqa main eik saal ki oontni ho to us se yehi qubul kar li jaaeygii lekin sadqa wasul karney wala usey bees dirham ya do bakriyan ata kerega, agar farz karen uskey paas eik saal ki oontni nahin balke uskey paas eik saal ka oont ho to us se usey wasul kar liya jaeyga aur uskey sath kuch aur nahin hoga, aur charney wali bakriyon ke barey mein sadqa ki sharah is tarah hai ke jab wo chaalis se eik so bees tak hon to un par eik bakri sadqa hai, aur jab eik so ikkis se do so tak hon to un par do bakriyan hain, aur jab do so se teen so tak hon to un par teen bakriyan hain, aur jab teen so se zayed ho jaeyn to phir her so par eik bakri hai, aur agar kisi charwahey ki bakriyan chaalis se kam (untaalees bhi) ho gaeen to un par Zakat nahin haan agar unka Malik apni marzi se chahey to nafli sadqa kar sakta hai, sadqe mein boodhi bakri, aebdaar aur saand nahin diya jaeyga magar jo sadqa wasul karney wala chahey, aur sadqe ke andheshey ke peshe-nazar mutafarriq maal ko jama kya jaey na ikhattey maal ko mutafarriq kya jaey, aur jo maal do sharikon ka ikhatta ho to wo Zakat b-qadr hissey barabar ada karen, chaandi mein chaaliswan hissey hai, aur agar chaandi sirf eik so nawwey dirham ho to is par koi Zakat nahin siwaey iske ki uska Malik ada karna chahey .'' Bukhari ."
1797,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis kheti ko barish ya chashma sairab karta ho ya wo kheti khud b-khud sairab ho to is mein ushr ( daswan hissey ( hai aur jisey kunwen ke pani se seencha jaey to is mein nisf ushr ( beeswaan) hissey hai.'' Bukhari ."
1798,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''janwer ka zakhm maaf hai (us par koi diyat w tawaan nahin), kunwen mein aur kaan mein maut waqey ho jaey to is par koi moawza nahin, aur dafeeney par paanchwan hissey Zakat hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1799,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine ghodey aur ghulam ( ki Zakat (ke barey mein darguzar farmaya , tum her chaalis dirham chaandi par eik dirham Zakat do, eik so nawwey dirham par koi Zakat nahin, jab do so dirham ho jaeyn to un par paanch dirham hain.'' Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood. aur Haris al-Aawar an Ali ki sanad se Abu-Dawood ki riwayat hai, Zuhair bayan kartey hain, mera khayal hai ke ye hadees Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se marwi (bayan) hai ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' chaaliswan hissey laao, her chaalis dirham par eik dirham hai, aur jab tak do so dirham na ho jaeyn tum par kuch bhi farz nahin, jab do so dirham ho jaeyn to un par paanch dirham Zakat hai, jab dirham ziyada hotey jaeyn to phir usi hisab se Zakat hogi , bakriyon ke barey mein hai ke her chaalis bakriyon par eik bakri hai, aur ye eik so bees bakriyon tak eik hi hai, aur eik so ikkis se do so tak do bakriyan hain, do so eik se teen so tak teen bakriyan hain, jab teen so se zayed ho jaeyn to phir her so par eik bakri hai, agar untaalees bakriyan hon to un par tumharey zimme koi Zakat nahin, aur gaey ke barey mein her tees gaey par gaey ka eik saala bacha hai, aur chaalis par do saala bacha hai, jabkey kheti-baadi waghera ka kaam karney waley janweron par Zakat wajib nahin.''"
1800,Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen Yamen ki taraf bheja to aapney unhen (mujhey) gaey ke mutalliq hukm farmaya ke her tees par gaey ka eik saala nar ya mada bachcha wasul karey aur her chaalis par do saala bacha.''
1801,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Zakat wasul karney mein ziyadti karney wala, Zakat na deney waley ki tarah hai.''"
1802,Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''paanch wasq se kam ghalley aur khajoor par koi Zakat nahin.'' rawahu Nasai.
1803,"Hazrat Musa bin Talha (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, hamarey paas Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ki wo tehreer hai jo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen ata ki thi, jis mein unhoney unko hukm farmaya tha ke gehun, jo, munaqqa aur khajoor mein se Zakat li jaey."
1804,Hazrat Itab bin Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne angooron ki Zakat ke mutalliq farmaya : ''khajuron ki tarah unka andaza kya jaeyga phir unki Zakat munaqqa se ada ki jaeygi jis tarah khajuron ki Zakat chhuwaron se ada ki jati hai.''
1805,"Hazrat Suhel bin abi Hashma ne hadees bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : ''jab tum andaza kar lo to phir Zakat wasul karo tihai hissey chhod do, agar tum tihai hissey na chhodo to phir chothai chhod do.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai."
1806,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Abdullah bin Rawaha (Raziallahu anhu) ko yahudiyon ke paas bheja kartey they, jab khajuron mein mithaas aa jati aur wo abhi khaney ke qabil na hotin to wo unka andaza kartey they."
1807,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne shehad ke barey mein farmaya : ''her das mishkizon (kanastaron) par eik mishkiza Zakat hai.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : iski sanad par kalam kya gaya hai, aur is barey mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se koi ziyada sahih chiz Sabit nahin. rawahu Tirmizi ."
1808,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki ehliya Zenab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen khutba irshad farmaya to farmaya : ''khawatin ki jamaat! sadqa karo, chahey apney zewrat se karo, kyonkey roze-qiyamat jahannam main tum ziyada hongi.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
1809,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke do aurten Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin to unke haathon mein soney ke do kangan they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se puchha : ''kya tum is (soney) ki Zakat ada karti ho?'' unhoney arz kya, ji nahin, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen farmaya : kya tum pasand karti ho ke Allah tumhen aag ke do kangan pehna dey ? unhoney arz kya, nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''to phir is soney ki Zakat ada karo.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : Musanna bin Sabaah ne is hadees ko Amr bin Shuaib se isi tarah riwayat kya hai, jabkey Musanna bin Sabaah aur ibn Lahiya dono hadees mein zaeef hain, us barey mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se koi chiz sahih Sabit nahin. rawahu Tirmizi ."
1810,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, main soney ke paazeb pehna karti thi, maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! kya ye bhi khazana hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo maal Zakat ke nisab ko pahunch jaey aur uski Zakat ada kar di jaey to phir wo khazana nahin.''"
1811,Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamen hukm diya kartey they ke ham tijarat ke liye tayyar kiye gaey maal ki Zakat ada karen.
1812,"Hazrat Rabeea bin abi Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) bahut se Sahaba se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Bilal bin Haris al-Muzni (Raziallahu anhu) ko qabeele ki kaanein ata farmaain aur ye faraa ki taraf hain, aur un se aaj tak sirf Zakat hi wasul ki jati hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
1813,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sabziyon, Atiya karda phal daar darakhton, paanch wasq se kam anaj, istimal mein aaney waley maweshiyon aur '' جبھہ '' par Zakat nahin .'' saqar raawi ne bataya : '' جبھہ '' se ghodey , khachar aur ghulam murad hain."
1814,"Hazrat Taaus (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas nisab se kam gaeyn laai gaeen to unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us barey mein mujhey kuch nahin farmaya. daarqutni, Shafai, aur unhoney farmaya : ''waqs'' se murad wo tadaad hai jo nisab tak na pahunchey ."
1815,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne musalmanon ke her ghulam w azad, mard w aurat aur chhotey badey par, eik saa khajoor ya eik saa (taqreeban dhaai kilo) jo sadqa fitr farz farmaya, aur uskey mutalliq hukm farmaya ke usey Namaz eid ke liye rawana honey se pehley ada kar diya jaey. muttafaq aleh."
1816,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham eik saa anaj, ya eik saa jo ya eik saa khajoor ya eik saa paneer ya eik saa kishmish sadqa fitr ada kya kartey they. muttafaq aleh."
1817,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Ramazan ke aakhir mein farmaya : apney rozon ka sadqa nikalo, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us sadqa ko eik saa khajoor ya eik saa jo ya aadha saa gehun par , azad ya ghulam , her mard w aurat aur har chhotey badey par farz farmaya."
1818,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sadqa fitr, rozon ko laghw, fohsh baaton se tahaarat aur miskinon ke liye khaney ke taur par farz farmaya. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
1819,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur unhoney apney dada se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik manadi karney waley ko Makka ke bazaron mein bheja ke wo aelan karey : '' sun lo ! sadqa fitr do mud (taqreeban sawa kilo) gehun ya eik saa doosra anaj her musalman mard w zan, azad w ghulam aur chhotey badey par wajib hai.''"
1820,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Solba ya Solba bin Abdullah bin Ubai Saeer apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''eik saa gehun her do par wajib hai, chhota ho ya bada, azad ho ya ghulam, mard ho ya aurat, raha tumhara maal daar shakhs to Allah uska tazkiya farma dega aur raha tumhara mohtaj shakhs to usko diye huey se ziyada diya jaeyga.''"
1821,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne raastey mein padi hui eik khajoor dekhi to farmaya : ''agar mujhey uskey sadqa ke honey ka andesha na hota to main usey kha leta.'' muttafaq aleh."
1822,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Hasan bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne sadqa ki khajuron mein se eik khajoor li aur usey munh mein dal liya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''thehrao, thehrao.'' taake wo usey phenk den, phir farmaya : ''kya tumhen malum nahin ke ham sadqa nahin khatey.'' muttafaq aleh."
1823,"Hazrat abdul-Muttalib bin Rabeea (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye sadqaat to logon (ke maal ka ( mail kuchail hai, aur ye Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aale-Muhammad ke liye halal nahin.'' rawahu Muslim ."
1824,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein koi khaney ki chiz pesh ki jati to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey mutalliq daryaft farmatey : ''kya ye hadiya hai ya sadqa ? ''agar bataya jata ke sadqa hai to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney Sahaba se farmatey : ''tum khaao .'' aur aap khud na khatey , aur agar bataya jata ke hadiya hai to aap apna haath badhaatey aur unke sath khatey . muttafaq aleh."
1825,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ki wajeh se teen ehkam shariyat ka pata chala , unhen azad kya gaya to unhen apney khawind ke mutalliq ikhtiyar diya gaya, aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wala ( haq virasat ( azad karney waley ko milega .'' aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghar tashrif laye to handiya mein gosht ubal raha tha, pas roti aur ghar ka salan aap ki khidmat mein pesh kya gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya maine handiya mein gosht nahin dekha ? ehle khana ne arz kya, kyon nahin, zarur dekha hai, lekin wo gosht Barira ko sadqa mein diya gaya hai jabkey aap sadqa tanaawul nahin farmatey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo uskey liye sadqa hai jabkey hamarey liye hadiya hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1826,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hadiya qubul kya kartey they aur uskey badley mein hadiya diya bhi kartey they. Bukhari."
1827,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar mujhey dasti ke gosht ki dawat di jaey to main zarur qubul karunga aur agar mujhey dasti ka gosht bator hadiya pesh kya jaey to main qubul karunga .'' Bukhari ."
1828,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' miskeen wo nahin jo eik ya do luqmon ya eik do khajuron ki khatir logon se sawal karta phirey, lekin miskeen wo hai jo is qadr khushhal nahin ke wo usey be-niaz kar dey aur uskey mutalliq pata bhi na chaley ke is par sadqa kya ja sakey aur wo logon se maangey bhi nahin .'' muttafaq aleh."
1829,"Hazrat abu-Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bano makhzum qabiley ke eik shakhs ko sadqaat wasul karney ke liye bheja to usney abu-Raafe se kaha, aap merey sath chalen taake aap bhi is mein se hasil karen, to unhoney kaha : nahin, yahan tak ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar aap se daryaft kar lun, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur aap se puchha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' hamarey liye sadqa halal nahin, kyonkey qom ke azad karda ghulam bhi unhi ( qom (ke zimrey mein aatey hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
1830,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kisi maal daar shakhs aur taqat war sahih khilqat shakhs ke liye sadqa lena halal nahin .'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Darmi."
1831,"Hazrat Imam Ahmed, Imam Nasai aur Imam ibne-Maja ne usey Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai."
1832,"Hazrat Ubaidullah bin Adi bin khiyaar bayan kartey hain, do aadmiyon ne mujhey bataya ke wo Hajjatul-wadaa ke moqe par Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye, aap us waqt sadqa taqseem farma rahey they, unhoney aap se sadqe ki darkhast ki to aapney nazar utha kar hamein dekha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen taqatwar dekh kar farmaya : ''agar tum chaho to main tumhen dey deta hun lekin is mein kisi maal daar shakhs aur kamai ki taqat rakhney waley shakhs ke liye koi hissey nahin.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
1833,"Hazrat Ata bin Yasar (Raziallahu anhu) mursal riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' paanch ashkhaas ke siwa kisi maal daar shakhs ke liye sadqa halal nahin : Allah ki raah mein jihad karney wala, sadqaat wasul karney wala, kisi shakhs ko tawaan dena pad jaey, wo shakhs jo apney maal ke zariey us ( sadqa ki chiz ( ko kharid ley, ya wo shakhs jiska padosi miskeen ho aur usey sadqa diya jaey aur wo miskeen shakhs maal daar shakhs ko bator hadiya bhej dey.'' rawahu Malik w Abu-Dawood ."
1834,aur Abu-Dawood ki abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) riwayat mein hai : '' ya musafir .''
1835,"Hazrat Ziyad bin Haris Sadaai (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to maine aap ki baiat ki, unhoney eik taweel hadees bayan ki, eik aadmi aap ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney arz kya, mujhey sadqa mein se kuch den , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : '' sadqaat ke mamley mein Allah ne kisi Nabi ya uskey ilawa kisi shakhs ki taqseem ke hukm ko pasand nahin farmaya , balke us mamley mein usney khud hukm farmaya to usey aath ajza (parts) mein taqseem farmaya, agar to tum bhi un aath ajza (parts) (masaarif) mein se ho to main tumhen dey deta hun.''"
1836,"Hazrat Zaid bin Aslam bayan kartey hain, umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne doodh piya to wo unhen pasand aaya, unhoney us doodh pilaney waley shakhs se puchha : ye doodh kahan se (hasil kya) hai? usney bataya ke wo falan ghaat par gaya tha, wahan sadqa ke kuch oont they aur wo (charwahey) unhen pani pila rahey they, unhoney unka doodh doha to maine usey apney bartan mein dal liya , ye wo hai. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne apna haath ( halaq mein) dala aur qai kar di."
1837,"Hazrat Qabisa bin makhaariq (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine eik zamanat ki zimme daari ley li, to main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua taake uskey liye main aap se sawal karun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum thehrao yahan tak ke hamarey paas sadqa aa jaey to phir ham tumhari khatir sadqa ka hukm dengey .'' phir farmaya : '' Qabisa ! sirf teen ashkhaas ke liye sawal karna jayez hai, wo aadmi jisney zamanat ki haami bhari to uskey liye sawal karna jayez hai yahan tak ke wo usey ada kar dey , aur phir sawal na karey, eik wo aadmi jis ko aisi aafat aa jaey ke wo uskey maal ko tabah kar dey to uskey liye sawal karna jayez hai yahan tak ke wo apni guzraan durust kar ley , aur eik us aadmi ke liye sawal karna jayez hai ke wo faaqa mein mubtala hai, yahan tak ke uski qom mein se teen daanaa aadmi gawahi dey den ke falan aadmi waaqiatan faaqa mein mubtala hai to uskey liye sawal karna jayez hai yahan tak ke wo apni guzraan durust kar sakey, aur Qabisa! un teen Suraton ke ilawa sawal karna haram hai, aur agar koi sawal karta hai to wo haram khata hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
1838,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs maal badhaney ki khatir logon ke maal mein se sawal karta hai to wo angaarey mang raha hai, wo kam maangey ya ziyada.'' rawahu Muslim ."
1839,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aadmi logon se maangta rehta hai yahan tak ke jab wo roze-qiyamat pesh hoga to uskey chehrey par koi gosht nahin hoga.'' muttafaq aleh."
1840,"Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sawal karney mein peechey na pad jaya karo, Allah ki qasam! jab tum mein se koi shakhs sawal karkey mujh se koi chiz hasil kar leta hai, jabkey main usey na-pasand karta hun to phir main wo chiz usey dey bhi dun to is mein barkat nahin hoti.'' rawahu Muslim ."
1841,"Hazrat Zuber bin Awam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tum mein se koi shakhs apni rassi lekar ( jangal mein jaey) apni pusht par lakdiyon ka gatha la kar farokht karey, aur is tarah Allah uskey chehrey ko sawal karney se bacha ley, to ye uskey liye sawal karney se behtar hai, mumkin hai ke wo usey kuch den ya na den.'' Bukhari ."
1842,"Hazrat Hakim bin Hizam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sawal kya to aapney mujhey ata kar diya, phir maine aap se sawal kya to aapney mujhey ata kar diya, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : '' Hakim ! ye maal sar-sabz sheereen hai, jisney sakhawat nafs ke sath usey hasil kya to uskey liye is mein barkat di jati hai, aur jisney hirs w tama ke sath usey hasil kya to uskey liye is mein barkat nahin di jati , aur wo us shakhs ki manind hai jo khata hai lekin sair nahin hota, aur ooper wala haath nichley waley haath se behtar hai.'' Hakim (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! us zaat ki qism jisney aap ko haq ke sath Nabi banakar bheja ! main aap ke baad zindagi bhar kisi se koi chiz nahin maangunga.'' muttafaq aleh."
1843,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) member par tashrif farma they, aur aapney sadqa karney aur sawal karney se bachney ke liye fazaail bayan kartey huey farmaya : '' ooper wala haath nichley haath se behtar hai, aur ooper wala haath kharch karney wala hai jabkey nichlaa haath sawal karney wala hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1844,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ansaar ke kuch logon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sawal kya to aapney unhen ata kar diya yahan tak ke aap ke paas jo kuch tha wo khatam ho gaya, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey paas jo maal hota hai main usey tum se bacha kar nahin rakhta, aur jo shakhs sawal karney se bachta hai to Allah usey bacha leta hai, aur jo shakhs be niaz rehna chahey to Allah usey be niaz kar deta hai, jo shakhs sabr karta hai to Allah usey sabir bana deta hai, aur kisi shakhs ko sabr se behtar aur wasee tar koi chiz ata nahin ki gaee .'' muttafaq aleh."
1845,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mujhey koi maal ata kartey to main arz karta , aap usey mujh se ziyada zarurat mand ko ata kar den , to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey : ''usey ley lo , aur usey apney maal mein shamil kar lo aur usey sadqa karo, aur agar bin maangey aur baghair intizar kiye tumharey paas maal aa jaey to usey ley liya karo aur jo aisa na ho uskey peechey na pado.'' muttafaq aleh."
1846,"Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sawal karna kharaash hai, aadmi unki wajeh se apney chehrey par kharaashein daalta hai, jo chahey unhen apney chehrey par baqi rakhey aur jo chahey unhen tarak kar dey, albatta aadmi badshah se sawal karey ya kisi aisi chiz ke barey mein sawal karey jiskey baghair koi chaara na ho to phir sawal karna jayez hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi w Nasai."
1847,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs is qadr milkiyat rakhney ke bawajud logon se sawal karey jo usey sawal karney se be niaz kar dey to wo roze-qiyamat aaeyga to wo sawal uskey chehrey par kharaash ki tarah hoga.'' Sahaba ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! wo kitni miqdaar hai jo usey sawal karney se be-niaz kar sakti hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''pachas dirham ya uskey barabar sona.''"
1848,"Hazrat Suhel bin Khizliya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs is qadr milkiyat rakhney ke bawajud sawal karey jo usey sawal karney se be niaz kar sakti ho to phir wo aag mein izafa kar raha hai.'' aur Nufaili jo us riwayat ke raawi hain, unhoney doosrey maqam par farmaya : wo maal ki kitni miqdaar hai jiskey hotey huey sawal karna munasib nahin? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo subh w Sham khaney ki miqdaar .'' aur eik doosrey maqam par farmaya : '' jiskey paas itna maal ho jo uski subh Sham ki shikam sairi ke liye kafi ho.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
1849,"Hazrat Ata bin Yasar (Raziallahu anhu) banu-Asad qabiley ke eik aadmi se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se jo shakhs auqiya ya uskey barabar chaandi ki milkiyat rakhney ke bawajud sawal karta hai to wo chimat kar sawal karney walon ke zimrey mein aata hai.'' rawahu Malik w Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
1850,"Hazrat Habshi bin Junada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maal daar shakhs ke liye sawal karna jayez hai na kaam karney ki taqat rakhney waley sahih khilqat shakhs ke liye, albatta us shakhs ke liye sawal karna jayez hai jo intehai mohtaj ho ya tawaan taley dab gaya ho, aur jo shakhs apna maal badhaney ki khatir logon se sawal karta hai to roze-qiyamat uskey chehrey par kharaash hogi, aur wo jahannam mein garm pathar khayega, jo chahey kam karey jo chahey ziyada karey.''"
1851,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke ansaar mein se eik aadmi sawal karney ki gharz se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tumharey ghar mein koi chiz nahin ? usney arz kya, kyon nahin, eik taat hai jo hamara odhna bichona hai aur eik piyala hai jis mein ham pani peetey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''unhen merey paas laao .'' wo unhen aap ke paas laya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen apney haath mein lekar farmaya : ''unhen kon kharidta hai? '' eik aadmi ne arz kya, main unhen eik dirham mein kharidta hun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do ya teen martaba farmaya : '' dirham se ziyada kon badhta hai? '' phir kisi aur aadmi ne kaha : main unhen do dirham mein kharidta hun, aapney wo dono chizen usey dey din aur do dirham lekar us Ansari ko diye aur farmaya : ''un mein se eik ka khana lekar apney ghar walon ke supurd karo aur doosrey se eik kulhaada lekar merey paas aao.'' pas wo usey lekar aap ki khidmat mein hazir hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney haath se is mein dasta lagaya, phir farmaya : '' ja aur lakdiyan ikhatti kar aur farokht kar aur main pandarah roz tak tumhen na dekhun.'' wo aadmi gaya aur lakdiyan ikhatti karkey farokht karta raha, wo aap ki khidmat mein hazir hua to uskey paas das dirham ho chukey they, usney kuch raqam ke kapdey khareedey aur kuch se ghalla kharid to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye tumharey liye us se behtar hai ke tum sawal karo aur roze-qiyamat tumharey chehrey par nukta ho, kyonkey sirf teen ashkhaas, intehai mohtaj shakhs, tawaan taley dabey huey shakhs aur diyat ki takleef se dochaar shakhs ke liye sawal karna jayez hai.'' Abu-Dawud, aur ibne-Maja ne ''roze-qiyamat'' ke alfaz tak bayan kya hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja ."
1852,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs faaqey mein mubtala ho jaey aur wo usey logon par pesh karey to uska faaqa door nahin hoga, aur jo shakhs uskey mutalliq Allah se arz karey to qarib hai ke Allah jald maut de-kar ya b-der dolat mandi de-kar usey ghani ata farma dey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi."
1853,"Hazrat ibne-Farasi apney baap se riwayat bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! main sawal kar liya karun? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nahin, agar tum ne zarur hi maangna ho to phir Saleh logon se sawal kya kar .''"
1854,"Hazrat ibn Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey sadqaat wasul karney par maamoor farmaya , jab main us ( kaam ( se farigh hua , aur wo unke supurd kar diye to unhoney tankhwaah leney ke liye mujhey hukm farmaya , to maine arz kya, maine to mehaz Allah ki khatir ye kaam kya tha aur mera ajr Allah ke zimmey hai, unhoney farmaya , jo diya jaey usey qubul kar, kyonkey maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke ehad mein ye kaam kya tha to aapney bhi mujhey tankhwaah pesh ki to maine bhi tumhari tarah hi arz kya tha, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya tha : ''jab bin maangey koi chiz tumhen di jaey to usey khaao aur sadqa karo.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
1855,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Arfa ke roz eik aadmi ko logon se sawal kartey huey suna to unhoney farmaya : kya tum us roz us jagah Allah ko chhod kar kisi aur se mang rahey ho, unhoney durrey ke sath uski pitaai ki . rawahu rizeen ( )."
1856,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : logo ! tum jaan lo ke tamaa (lalach) faqr hai, jabkey ( logon sey) na-ummidi ghina hai, kyonkey jab aadmi kisi chiz se na ummid ho jata hai to wo us se be niaz ho jata hai. rawahu rizeen"
1857,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs mujhey zamanat dey ke wo logon se koi chiz nahin maangega to main usey jannat ki zamanat deta hun, Soban (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya, main (zamanat deta hun) aur aap kisi se koi chiz nahin maangtey they. rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
1858,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey bulaya jabkey aap mujh se shart qaaim kar rahe they ke tum ne logon se kisi chiz ke barey mein sawal nahin karna.'' maine arz kya, ji haan, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tumhara koda gir jaey to uska sawal bhi nahin karna yahan tak ke tum nichey utar kar khud usey pakdo.''"
1859,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar uhud pahad jitna sona merey paas ho to mujhey khushi hogi ke teen din ke baad is mein se kuch bhi merey paas baaqi na bachey bajuz uskey jisey mein qarz ki adaegi ke liye rakh lun.'' Bukhari ."
1860,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''har roz subah ke waqt do farishtey aasman se nazil hotey hain to un mein se eik kehta hai : aey Allah ! kharch karney waley ko badal ata farma jabkey doosra kehta hai : aey Allah ! bakheel ko tabahi se dochaar kar.'' muttafaq aleh."
1861,"Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kharch kar lekin shumar na kar warna Allah tujhey bhi gin gin kar dega, (maal ko) rok kar na rakh warna Allah tujh se rok lega aur jitna ho sakey ata karti raho.'' muttafaq aleh."
1862,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala farmata hai : ibne-Adam ! kharch kar , main tujh par kharch karunga.'' muttafaq aleh."
1863,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ibne-Adam ! agar to zayed az zarooriyaat kharch kar dey to wo terey liye behtar hai, aur agar to usey roke rakhey to wo terey liye bura hai, lekin zarurat ke mutabiq rakh leney par tujh par koi malamat nahin, aur apney zere-kafalat afrad par pehley kharch kar.'' rawahu Muslim."
1864,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bakheel aur sadqa karney waley ki misal un do aadmiyon ki si misal hai jin par lohey ki zirhen hain, aur unke haath unke seeney aur hansli tak bandhey huey hain, jab sadqa karney wala sadqa karta hai to wo zireh kushada hoti chali jati hai, aur jab bakheel sadqa karney ka irada karta hai to wo tang ho jati hai aur her kadi apni jagah par aa jati hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1865,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''zulm se bacho, kyonkey zulm roze-qiyamat andheron ka baais hoga, aur mazeed ki hirs (bukhl) se bacho kyonkey usney tum se pehley logon ko halak kiya, aur baham (aapas mein) qatl aur gharat karney aur muhaarim ko halal karney par unhen aamada kiya.'' rawahu Muslim."
1866,"Hazrat Harisa bin Wahab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sadqa kiya karo kyonkey tum par aisa waqt bhi aaeyga ke aadmi apna sadqa liye phirega lekin wo aisa shakhs nahin paeyga jo usey qubul kar ley , aadmi (jiskey paas wo jaeyga) kahega : agar tum kal isey ley aatey to main isey qubul kar leta jabkey aaj mujhey iski koi zarurat nahin.'' muttafaq aleh."
1867,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! ajr aur sawab ke lihaz se kon sa sadqa sab se behtar hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo sadqa jo to tandurusti mein karey jabkey maal ki hirs tum par ghalib ho, aur tujhey faqr ka andesha bhi ho aur tawangari ka tamaa (lalach) (dar) bhi, aur (sadqa karney mein) der na kar yahan tak ke jab saans halaq tak pahunch jaey aur to kahe : itna maal falan ke liye aur itna falan ke liye jabkey wo to (khud se) falan ka ho chuka.'' muttafaq aleh."
1868,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua jabkey aap Kaba ke saye taley tashrif farma they, jab aapney mujhey dekha to farmaya : ''rabe-Kaaba ki qism ! wo nuqsan uthaney waley hain.'' maine arz kiya, merey waliden aap par qurban hon, wo kon hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo ziyada maal waley, lekin wo log jinhonne kaha is taraf bhi, is taraf bhi aur us taraf bhi, apney aa gaey, apney peechhey aur apney daain , apney baain , jabkey aisey log kam hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
1869,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sakhi shakhs Allah ke qarib hai, jannat ke qarib aur logon ke qarib hai aur jahannam se baeed hai, jabkey bakheel shakhs Allah se door , jannat se baeed , logon se baeed aur jahannam ke qarib hai, aur jahil sakhi Allah ko abid bakheel se ziyada pasand hai.''"
1870,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar koi shakhs apni zindagi main eik dirham sadqa karta hai to ye uskey liye qaribul-marg (maut ke qareeb) so dirham sadqa karney se behtar hai.''"
1871,"Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo shakhs jo apni maut ke qarib sadqa karta hai ya ghulam azad karta hai to wo us shakhs ki tarah hai jo pet bharey honey ke baad hadiya karey.'' Ahmed, Nasai , Darmi , aur unhoney usey sahih qarar diya hai. rawahu Ahmed w Nasai w Darmi ."
1872,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' bukhl aur bad-akhlaqi jaisi khaslatein kisi momin mein jama nahin ho saktin.''"
1873,"Hazrat abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' fasad w ladaai paida karney wala, bakheel aur ehsan jatlaaney wala shakhs jannat mein dakhil nahin hoga.''"
1874,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aadmi mein intehai hirs aur intehai buzdili jaisi khaslatein buri hain.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
1875,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki baaz paak biviyon (paak biwiyon) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kiya, ham mein se sab se pehley aap se kon milen gi? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se jiskey haath ziyada daraz hain.'' wo lakdi lekar apney bazu naapney lagen , to Sauda (Raziallahu anha) ke haath un mein se ziyada daraz they, phir hamen baad mein pata chala ke unke haath lambey honey se murad , sadqa thi, aur ham mein se Zenab (Raziallahu anhu) sab se pehley aap se ja milin, aur wo sadqa karna pasand kiya karti thin . Bukhari aur sahih Muslim ki riwayat mein hai : Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein lambey haath wali mujhey sab se pehley mileygi.'' wo bayan karti hain : wo ye janney ke liye un mein se kis ke haath daraz hain wo baham (aapas mein) haath naapaa karti thin, isliye Zenab (Raziallahu anhu) ke ham mein se haath ziyada lambey they, kyonkey wo apney haath se kaam kiya karti thin. muttafaq aleh."
1876,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kisi aadmi ne kaha : main sadqa karunga , wo apna sadqa lekar bahar nikla to usney usey kisi chor ke haath mein thamaa diya, subah hui to baaten honey lagin ke raat kisi chor par sadqa kar diya gaya, to us aadmi ne kaha : aey Allah ! her qism ki hamd terey hi liye hai, kisi chor par (sadqa kar diya gaya) , main zarur sadqa karunga , wo sadqa lekar nikla aur usey kisi zaaniya ke haath par rakh diya, subah hui to baaten honey lagin ke raat kisi zaaniya par sadqa kar diya gaya, phir us aadmi ne kaha : aey Allah ! her qism ki hamd terey hi liye hai, ( maine ( kisi zaaniya par) sadqa kar diya ( , main zarur sadqa karunga , wo sadqa lekar nikla aur aur kisi maal daar shakhs ke haath mein dey diya, subah hui to log badey tajjub se baaten karney lagey ke raat kisi maal daar par sadqa kar diya gaya, usney kaha : aey Allah ! her qism ki hamd terey hi liye hai, ( maine ( chor , zaaniya aur maal daar shakhs par) sadqa kar diya ( usey khuwab mein bataya gaya, tum ne jo chor par sadqa kiya to mumkin hai ke wo chori karney se baaz aa jaey, rahi zaaniya to mumkin hai ke wo zina-kaari se baaz aa jaey, aur raha maal daar shakhs to shayad ke wo ibrat hasil karey aur Allah ke ata karda maal mein se kharch karey.'' Bukhari , Muslim , aur alfaze-hadees Imam Bukhari ke hain. muttafaq aleh."
1877,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''is beech main eik aadmi sehra (registaan) mein tha ke usney badalon main eik aawaz suni ke falan shakhs ke baagh ko sairab karo, wo badal (wahan sey) alag hua aur usney apna pani sangrezon wali zamin par barsaya , to un naaliyon mein se eik naali ne wo sara pani samet liya , phir wo aadmi pani ke peechey-peechey gaya to dekha ke eik aadmi apney baagh mein khada apni kassi ke zariey pani ka (bahaaw ke) rukh badal raha hai, us aadmi ne us se puchha : Allah ke bandey ! tumhara naam kya hai? usney kaha : falan , usney bilkul wohi naam bataya jo usney badalon mein suna tha, us aadmi ne kaha : Allah ke bandey ! tum ne mera naam kyon puchha hai? usney kaha : maine us badal mein , jis ka ye pani hai, eik aawaz suni ke wo tumhara naam lekar keh raha tha, falan shakhs ke baagh ko sairab karo, tum is mein kya kartey ho? usney kaha : jo tum ne keh diya, to ab suno , main iski pedawar ka tihai hissey sadqa karta hun, tihai hissey main aur merey ehale w ayaal khatey hain aur uska tihai hissey is (baagh) par kharch kar deta hun.'' rawahu Muslim."
1878,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''bani Israel ke teen aadmi they, baras (safed daagh) mein mubtala shakhs, ganjaa aur andha , Allah ne unhen aazmaney ka irada farmaya to unki taraf eik farishta bheja , wo baras ke mareez shakhs ke paas aaya to kaha tumhen kon si chiz ziyada pasand hai? usney kaha : achchha rang aur khoobsurat jild, aur ye bimari mujh se hata di jaey, jiski wajeh se log mujhey na pasand kartey hain, raawi bayan kartey hain, usney is par haath phera to uska marz jata raha , aur usey behtareen rangat aur behtareen jild ata kar di gaee , us ( farishtey ( ne puchha : tumhen kon sa maal ziyada mehbub hai? usney kaha : oont ya usney kaha gaaey.'' Is'haq raawi ko shak hua ke baras ke mareez aur ganjey un dono mein se eik ne oont kaha aur doosrey ne gaaey kaha, farmaya : ''usey das maah ki hamila oontni de-di gaee to us ( farishtey ( ne kaha : Allah inke barey main tumhen barkat ata farmaey.'' raawi bayan kartey hain : '' phir wo ganjey ke paas gaya to usney kaha : tumhen kon si chiz ziyada pasand hai? usney kaha : khoobsurat zulfein aur mujh se ye takleef door kar di jaey jiski wajeh se log mujhey na pasand kartey hain.'' raawi ne kaha : ''usney is par haath phera to wo takleef jati rahi , usey khoobsurat zulfein ata kar di gaeen, phir usney puchha : tumhen kon sa maal ziyada mehbub hai? usney kaha : gaaey, usey eik hamila gaaey de-di gaee aur farishtey ne kaha : Allah is main tumhen barkat ata farmaai , raawi ne kaha : phir wo naa-beeney shakhs ke paas gaya to kaha : tumhen kon si chiz ziyada mehbub hai? usney kaha : Allah mujhey meri basaarat lota dey taake main uskey zariey logon ko dekh sakoon.'' raawi ne kaha : ''usney is par haath phera to Allah ne usey uski basaarat lauta di, phir usney puchha : tumhen kon sa maal ziyada pasand hai? usney kaha bakriyan , phir usey hamila bakri de-di gaee , phir oont , gaaey aur bakri ne bachchey diye , to us (baras waley) ke yahan wadi bhar oont ho gaey, uskey (ganjey) yahaan wadi bhar gaaey ho gaeen aur us ( naa-beeney (ke yahan wadi bhar bakriyan ho gaee.'' raawi bayan kartey hain : '' phir wo ( farishta ( usi surat aur haiyat mein baras mein mubtala shakhs ke paas aaya to usney kaha : miskeen aadmi hun, dorane-safar asbab khatam ho chukey hain, aaj mujhey sirf Allah ka sahara hai ya phir main tum se us zaat ke wastey se sawal karta hun, jisney tujhey behtareen rangat aur behtareen jild aur maal ata kiya, ke tum mujhey eik oont dey do jiskey zariey main apni manzil par pahunch jaaunga, us shakhs ne kaha : huquq bahut ziyada hain, (kis kis ko dun), us (farishtey) ne kaha : aisey lagta hai ke main tumhen pehchanta hun, kya tum baras mein mubtala nahin they, log tujhey na pasand kartey they aur tum faqir they, Allah ne tumhen maal ata kiya, us shakhs ne kaha : ye maal to mujhey baap- daada se mila hai, us farishtey ne kaha : agar tum jhootey ho to Allah tumhen pehley ki tarah kar dega.'' raawi bayan kartey hain : ''phir wo apni usi surat mein ganjey shakhs ke paas gaya to usney usey bhi wohi baat kahi jo usney us (baras waley) se kahi thi, aur usney wesay hi jawab diya jaisey us shakhs ne jawab diya tha, farishtey ne kaha : agar tum jhootey ho to Allah tumhen phir pehley ki tarah kar dey.'' raawi bayan kartey hain : ''phir wo apni usi surat aur haiyat mein naa-beeney shakhs ke paas gaya to kaha : miskeen aadmi aur musafir hun, merey dorane-safar asbab munqata' (khatam) ho gaey hain, aaj manzil tak pahunchney ke liye mujhey Allah ka sahara hai, aur phir main tum se us zaat ka wasila bana kar sawal karta hun jisney tumhari beenai lautaai ke tum eik bakri dey do, jiskey zariey main apni manzil par pahunch jaaunga, us shakhs ne kaha : yaqinan main eik na-bina shakhs tha, Allah ne meri beenai lauta di, jo chaho ley jaao aur chaho chhod jaao, Allah ki qism ! aaj jo kuchh tum Allah ki khatir uthaaoge is par main tum par koi sakhti nahin karunga , us ( farishtey ( ne kaha : apna maal apney paas rakho , tumhari to aazmaaish ki gaee thi, Allah Taala tum par razi ho gaya aur terey do sathiyon par naraz ho gaya.'' muttafaq aleh."
1879,"Hazrat Umme-Bujeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! miskeen merey darwazey par khada ho jata hai yahan tak ke mujhey haya aati hai ke main uskey haath par rakhney ke liye ghar mein koi chiz nahin paati , to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''uskey haath par kuch na kuch rakh diya karo chahey (chaahe) jala hua khir hi kyon na ho.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ''ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. rawahu Ahmed, Abu-Dawood aur Tirmizi."
1880,"Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke azad karda ghulam bayan kartey hain, Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ko gosht ka eik tukda bator hadiya pesh kiya gaya jabkey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko gosht pasand tha, to unhoney khaadima se farmaya : isey ghar mein rakho shayad ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) isey tanaawul farmaain (khaaeyn), usney usey ghar ke taaq mein rakha , aur itney mein saail darwazey par aa kar khada ho gaya aur kehney laga : Allah tumhen barkat ata farmaai , sadqa karo . ehale khana ne bhi kaha : Allah tumhen barkat ata farmaai (yani tumhara bhala ho) , wo saail chala gaya, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif ley aaye , aapney farmaya : ''Umme-Salma ! kya tumharey paas koi chiz hai ke main usey kha lun?'' unhoney arz kiya, ji haan , aur khaadima se farmaya : jaao aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye wo gosht laao , wo gaee to wahan taaq mein (gosht ke bajaey) sirf eik safed pathar pada hua tha, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo gosht , safed pathar bin gaya, tum ne usey saail ko kyon na diya?''"
1881,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya main tumhen maqam aur martabe ke lihaz se bad-tareen shakhs ke barey mein na bataaun ?'' arz kya gaya, ji haan , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis se Allah ke naam par sawal kiya jaey aur wo na dey.'' rawahu Ahmed."
1882,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Usman (Raziallahu anhu) se andar janey ki ijazat talab ki to unhoney unhen ijazat de-di , aur unke haath main eik lathi thi, to Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Kab ! Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) wafat pa gaey aur unhoney maal chhoda hai, is barey main tumhara kya khayal hai? unhoney kaha : agar to wo is barey mein Allah ka haq ada kiya kartey they to phir koi harj nahin, Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne lathi uthai aur Kab ko dey maari , aur kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''main ye pasand nahin karta ke agar merey paas us pahad barabar sona ho aur main usey kharch kar dun aur wo mujh se qubul bhi ho jaey aur phir main apney peechhey chhe auqiya chhod jaaun.'' Usman ! main tumhen Allah ki qism deta hun, kya aapney isey suna hai? teen martaba kaha, unhoney farmaya : haan."
1883,"Hazrat Aqba bin Haris (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Madina mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechhey namaze-Asr ada ki to aap salam pher kar khadey huey aur tezi ke sath logon ki gardanen phlaangte huey apni baaz paak biviyon (biwiyon) ke hujron ki taraf tashrif ley gaey, Sahaba kiram aap ki us tezi aur jaldi se pareshan ho gaey jab aap unke paas wapis tashrif laye aur aapney dekha ke unhoney aap ki tezi par tajjub kiya hai, aapney farmaya : ''mujhey soney ki eik dalee (tukda) yad aa gaee jo hamarey paas thi, mujhey nagawar guzra ke wo mujhey Allah ki yad se rokey rakhey , lihaza maine uski taqseem ka hukm farma diya .'' Bukhari , aur Sahih Bukhari ki dusri riwayat mein hai, farmaya : ''maine sadqe ki soney ki dali ghar chhodi thi, maine usey raat bhar ghar rakhna na-pasand kiya. Bukhari."
1884,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke unhoney kaha, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bimar huey to merey paas aap ke chhe ya saat Dinar they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey hukm farmaya ke main unhen taqseem kar dun, lekin Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki takleef ne mujhey masroof rakha , aapney unke mutalliq phir mujh se puchha : ''aapney un chhe ya saat dinaaron ka kya kiya?'' maine arz kiya, Allah ki qism ! aap ki takleef ne mujhey masroof kar diya, unhoney wo mangaaey, phir unhen apni hatheli mein rakha , farmaya : ''Allah ka Nabi kya guman karey ke wo Shan Wale Allah se mulaqat karey aur ye uskey paas hon.'' rawahu Ahmed."
1885,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas tashrif ley gaey to us waqt khajuron ka eik dher unke paas tha, aapney farmaya : ''Bilal ! ye kya hai? '' unhoney arz kiya, maine kal ke liye kuch zakhira kiya tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum dartey nahin ke kal roze-qiyamat to isey jahannam ki aag dekhega , Bilal ! kharch kar aur arsh wali zaat se muflisi ka andesha na kar.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan) ."
1886,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sakhaawat , jannat main eik darkht hai, isliye jo shakhs sakhi hoga to wo uski eik shaakh ko pakad lega , phir shaakh usey nahin chodeygi yahan tak ke wo usey jannat mein ley jaeygi, jabkey bakheeli aur tamaa (lalach) (lalach) jahannam ka eik darkht hai jo shakhs bakheel hoga to wo uski eik shaakh pakad lega , aur wo shaakh usey nahin chodeygi yahan tak ke usey jahannam mein ley jaeygi.''"
1887,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sadqa karney mein jaldi kiya karo, kyonkey balaa aur musibat us se aagey nahin pahunch sakti.'' rawahu Razeen."
1888,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs halal kamai se khajoor ke barabar sadqa karta hai, jabkey Allah sirf halal maal hi qubul karta hai, to Allah usey apney daain haath mein qubul farmata hai, phir usey uskey Malik ke liye is tarah badhata hai jis tarah tum mein se koi apney ghodey ke bachchey ki parwarish karta hai, yahan tak ke wo pahad ki manind ho jati hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1889,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sadqe se maal kam nahin hota, darguzar karney aur maaf kar deney se Allah bandey ki izzat mein izafa farmata hai, aur jo koi Allah ki khatir tawaazeh (mahman-nawazi) ikhtiyar karta hai to Allah usko rifat (bulandi) ata farmata hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
1890,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne kisi chiz ka joda Allah ki raah mein kharch kiya to usey jannat ke darwazon se bulaya jaeyga, aur jannat ke (aath) darwazey hain, jo shakhs namazi hoga usey (باب الصلوۃ) se dawat di jaeygi, jo Mujahid hoga usey (باب الجہاد) se aawaz di jaeygi, jo ehale sadqa mein se hoga usey (باب الصدقہ) se bulaya jaeyga, roze daar ko (باب الریان) se aawaz di jaeygi.'' Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya, wesay zaroori to nahin ke kisi ko un sab darwazon se bulaya jaey, phir bhi kya kisi ko un tamam darwazon se dawat di jaeygi? aapney farmaya : ''haan , main ummid karta hun ke aap unhi mein se hongey.'' muttafaq aleh."
1891,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aaj tum mein se kon rozey se hai? '' Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya : main , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aaj tum mein se kon janaazey ke sath shareek hua?'' Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya : main , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aaj tum mein se kis ne miskeen ko khana khilaya?'' Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya, maine , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aaj tum mein se kis ne mareez ki iyaadat ki?'' Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya : maine , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs mein ye khaslatein jama ho jaeyn to wo jannat mein dakhil ho jaeyga.'' rawahu Muslim."
1892,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''musalman khawatin ! koi padausan apni padausan ke kisi hadiye ko haqeer na samjhey chahey (chaahe) wo bakri ka khur hi ho.'' muttafaq aleh."
1893,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) aur Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''her maroof (bhali baat , bhala kalam) sadqa hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1894,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''neki ke kisi bhi kaam ko maamuli mat samjho , chahey tum apney bhai ko khanda peshani se (khush hokar) milo.'' rawahu Muslim."
1895,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''her musalman par sadqa karna wajib hai.'' Sahaba ne arz kiya, agar wo na paey? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney haathon se kamai karey aur apney aap ko faeyda pahunchaey aur sadqa karey.'' unhoney arz kiya, agar wo istataat na rakhey ya na kar paey? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''zarurat mand majbur shakhs ki madad karey.'' unhoney arz kiya : agar wo ye bhi na kar sakey? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''neki ka hukm karey.'' unhoney arz kiya, agar na kar sakey? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''burai se ruk jaey kyonkey ye bhi uskey liye sadqa hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1896,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''insan ke her jod par her roz sadqa karna wajib hai, do aadmiyon ke darmiyan adl karna sadqa hai, aadmi ki uski sawari ke barey mein madad karna , wo usey sawari par bithaaey ya uska saman is par rakhwaaey , ye bhi sadqa hai, achhi baat karna sadqa hai, Namaz ki taraf her qadam uthana sadqa hai, aur raastey se takleef deh chiz door kar dena sadqa hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1897,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''her insan ke teen sau saath jod hain jis shakhs ne (اللہ اکبر ، الحمد للہ ، لا الہ الا اللہ ، سبحان اللہ) aur (استغفر اللہ) kaha, aur logon ke raastey se pathar ya kaantay ya haddi ko door kar diya ya neki ka hukm ya burai se mana kiya aur ye kaam teen sau saath adad ke barabar kiya to wo us roz is tarah chalta hai ke usney apney aap ko jahannam se bacha liya hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
1898,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''her tasbih sadqa hai, her takbir sadqa hai, her tamheed sadqa hai, her tahleel (la Ilaah illallah) kehna sadqa hai, achchhi baat kehna sadqa hai, burai se mana karna sadqa hai aur tumhara apni ehliya se jima (sambhog) karna sadqa hai.'' unhoney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! kya ham mein se koi apni shehwat puri karta hai to is par usey ajr milega? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey bataao , agar wo haram tareeqey se shehwat puri karta to kya is par gunah hota? isi tarah jab wo halal tareeqey se usey pura kerega to usey ajr milega.'' rawahu Muslim."
1899,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''doodh deney wali behtareen oontni udhaar dena aur doodh deney wali behtareen bakri , jo subh aur Sham bartan bhar deti ho, udhaar dena behtareen sadqa hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1900,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab koi musalman shajr-kaari karta (paid lagata) hai ya kaashtkaari karta hai, phir koi insan ya perinda ya koi haiwaan is mein se kha leta hai to ye uskey liye sadqa hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1901,Aur Sahih Muslim mein Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai : ''jo is mein se chori ho jaey to wo bhi uskey liye sadqa hai.'' rawahu Muslim.
1902,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''eik bad-kar aurat ko bakhsh diya gaya ke wo kunwen ke kinarey eik kuttey ke paas se guzri jo ke apni zaban bahar nikaley haanp raha tha, qarib tha ke shiddat piyas usey halak kar daley, usney apna joota utara aur usey apney dupattey se baandh kar uskey liye pani nikala to usey us wajeh se bakhsh diya gaya.'' arz kiya gaya, kya Haiwaanon ke sath Husne-sulook (achchha sulook) karney se bhi hamarey liye ajr hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''her jaan daar chiz ke sath achchha sulook karney mein ajr hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1903,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''eik aurat ko eik billi ki wajeh se azab mein mubtala kiya gaya, usney usey baandh rakha tha, yahan tak ke wo bhook ki wajeh se mar gaee , usney khud usey khilaya na usey chhoda ke wo (keedey-makaudey) kha leti.'' muttafaq aleh."
1904,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''eik aadmi eik darkht ki shaakh ke paas se guzra jo ke raahe guzar par thi, usney kaha : main usey musalmanon ki raah se hata deta hun taake ye unhen takleef na pahunchaey , usey (is bina par) jannat mein dakhil kar diya gaya.'' muttafaq aleh."
1905,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine eik aadmi ko , eik darkht ki wajeh sey, jannat mein idhar-udhar phirtey dekha ke usney raahe-guzar se usey kaat diya tha jo ke logon ke liye takleef ka baais tha.'' rawahu Muslim."
1906,"Hazrat Abu-Barza (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kiya, Allah ke Nabi ! mujhey koi nafa mand chiz bataeyn , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''musalmanon ki guzar gaah se takleef deh chiz ko hata dey.'' an-qareeb ham Adi bin Hatim se marwi (bayan) hadees : ''dozakh se bachaaw ikhtiyar karo.'' ko In-sha-Allah taala baab alaamaate nabuwat mein zikr karengey. rawahu Muslim."
1907,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Salaam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madina tashrif laye to main bhi) aap ki ziyaarat ke liye ( aaya, jab maine ghor ke sath aap ka chehra Mubarak dekha to maine pehchan liya ke aap ka chehra kisi jhootey shakhs ka chehra nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sab se pehley farmaya : ''logo ! Islam aam karo, khana khilaoo, sila rehmi karo aur raat ke waqt , jabkey log so rahey hon, Namaz padho , (is tarah) tum salamti ke sath jannat mein dakhil ho jaaogey.'' rawahu Tirmizi, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
1908,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Rehman ki ibadat karo, khana khilaao aur salam aam karo, tum salamti ke sath jannat mein dakhil ho jaaogey.'' rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
1909,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak sadqa , rab ke ghazab ko khatam karta hai aur buri maut ko door karta hai.''"
1910,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' her maroof sadqa hai, tumhara apney bhai ko khanda peshani se milna aur tumhara apni baalti se apney bhai ke bartan mein pani dal dena bhi neki mein se hai.'' rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi ."
1911,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumhara apney bhai ko dekh kar tabassum farmana , neki ka hukm karna, burai se rokna, raah bhooley shakhs ki rahnumai karna, na-bina shakhs ki madad karna, pathar, kaantay aur haddi ko raastey se hata dena aur apney dol se kisi bhai ke dol mein pani dalna bhi sadqa hai.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
1912,"Hazrat Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! Umme- Saad (Raziallahu anhu) wafat pa chuki hain, ( unke liye ( kon sa sadqa karna afzal hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' pani .'' unhoney eik kunwan khudwaya aur farmaya : ye Umme- Saad ke liye hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
1913,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo musalman kisi nangey badan musalman ko libas pahnaaey to Allah usey jannat ka sabz (hara) libas pahnaaeyga aur jo musalman kisi bhookey musalman ko khana khilaaey to Allah usey jannat ke mewey khilaaeyga aur jo musalman kisi piyasey musalman ko pani palaey to Allah usey kastoori se seal band khalis sharab palaeyga .''"
1914,"Hazrat Fatima binte-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' maal mein Zakat ke ilawa bhi haq hai.'' phir aapney ye aayat tilawat farmaai : '' neki yehi nahin ke tum apney chehrey mashriq w maghrib ki taraf kar lo.''"
1915,"Hazrat Buhaisa apney walid se riwayat karti hain, unhoney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! wo kon si chiz hai jis se rokna jayez nahin ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' pani .'' unhoney phir arz kya : Allah ke Nabi ! wo kon si chiz hai jis se rokna jayez nahin ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' namak .'' unhoney phir arz kya, Allah ke Nabi ! wo kon si chiz hai jis se rokna jayez nahin ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye ke tum bhalai ke kaam karo, wo tumharey liye behtar hain.''"
1916,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs banjar zamin kaasht karta hai to uskey liye us (kaasht kerney) mein ajr hai, aur her Talibe-rizq is mein se jo kha jaey to wo uskey liye sadqa hai.'' rawahu Darmi ."
1917,"Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs doodh wala janwer udhar de-dey ya koi qarz de-dey ya kisi ko raasta bata dey to uskey liye ghulam azad karney ke barabar sawab hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
1918,"Hazrat Abu-Jari Jabir bin Saleem bayan kartey hain, main Madina aaya to maine eik aadmi ko dekha ke log uskey hukm ki taameel kartey hain, wo jo kehta hai wo is par amal kartey hain, maine puchha : ye kon shakhs hai? unhoney bataya : ye Allah ke Rasool hain. raawi bayan kartey hain, maine do martaba kaha : alaikassalaam ya Rasulullah ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''alaikassalam na kaho, alaikassalam to maiyat ke liye dua w salam hai, kaho , Assalamualaik .'' raawi bayan kartey hain, maine arz kya aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah ke Rasool hain? to aapney farmaya : ''main us Allah ka Rasool hun ke agar tumhen koi takleef pahunch jaey aur to us se dua karey to wo takleef ko tujh se door kar dey , aur agar to qehat saali mein mubtala ho jaey aur us se dua karey to wo tujhey sar-sabzi w shadabi ata farma dey , jab to kisi registaan ya sehra mein ho aur teri sawari gum ho jaey, phir to us se dua karey to wo usey wapis lota dey , maine arz kya : mujhey koi wasiyat farmaeyn, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kisi ko gaali na dena .'' raawi bayan kartey hain, maine phir uskey baad kisi azad ko gaali di na kisi ghulam ko na kisi oont ko na hi kisi bakri ko , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' neki ke kisi kaam ko haqeer na janna , agar to apney bhai se khanda peshani se guftgu karey to ye bhi neki hai, apna izaar nisf pindli tak rakh , agar to aisey na karey to phir takhnon tak , aur) takhnon se nichey ( izaar ( tehband , shalwaar, pajama waghera) latkaaney se ijtinab kar, kyonkey ye takabbur hai, aur Allah takabbur pasand nahin karta aur agar koi aadmi tujhey gaali dey aur tujh par aeb lagaey jiskey mutalliq wo janta ho ke wo ( aeb ( tum mein mojud hai, to uskey mutalliq jo tum jantey ho, is par aeb na lagaao uska wabal usi par hoga .'' Abu-Dawud, Imam Tirmizi ne is hadees se salam wala hissey riwayat kya hai aur eik riwayat mein hai : '' tumhen uska ajr milega jabkey is par wabal hoga .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi ."
1919,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai unhon (yani ehle bait ( ne eik bakri zibeh ki to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne daryaft farmaya : '' us se kuch bacha hai? '' unhoney arz kya : uski dasti bachi hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' uski dasti ke siwa baqi sab bach gaya hai.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney usey sahih qarar diya hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
1920,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jab koi musalman kisi musalman ko libas faraham karta hai to jab tak us libas ka eik tukda is par rehta hai to wo shakhs Allah ki hifazat mein rehta hai.''"
1921,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) marfoo riwayat bayan kartey hain, farmaya : '' teen ashkhaas hain jinhen Allah pasand karta hai, dorane-tahajjud Quran ki tilawat karney wala, daain haath se sadqa karney wala jo usey apney baaein hath se bhi makhfii rakhta hai, aur eik wo aadmi jo kisi lashkar mein ho aur uskey sathi shikast kha jaeyn lekin wo phir bhi dushman ke samney seena-sipar rahey .'' Tirmizi aur unhoney ne farmaya : ye hadees mehfooz nahin, uska eik raawi abu-Bakar bin Ayash, kasrat ke sath ghaltiyaan karta hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
1922,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' teen ashkhaas aisey hain jinhen Allah pasand karta hai aur teen aisey hain jinhen Allah na pasand karta hai, rahey wo jinhen Allah pasand karta hai to un mein se eik wo aadmi hai jo kisi qom ke paas jaey aur Allah ke naam par un se sawal karey, wo un se apni bahami (aapsi) qurbat ki wajeh se sawal na karey, lekin wo usey kuch na den , eik aadmi ne apney sathiyon se alag ho kar chhipey taur par usey kuch dey diya jisey sirf Allah janta hai aur wo leney wala janta hai, aur eik wo qom jo sari raat chalti rahi yahan tak ke jab neend unhen tamam chizon se ziyada mehbub ho gaee to wo so gaey is beech main eik aadmi khada ho kar khushu w khuzoo ke sath mujh se dua karney laga aur meri aayaat ki tilawat karney laga aur) teesra ( wo shakhs jo kisi lashkar mein dushman se barsare-paikaar ho lekin wo shikast kha jaeyn to ye phir bhi seena-sipar rahey yahan tak ke usey Shaheed kar diya jaey ya usey Fateh hasil ho jaey, aur wo teen jinhen Allah na pasand karta hai : boodha zaani , mutakabbir faqir aur zalim maaldaar hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Nasai ."
1923,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Allah ne zamin paida farmaai to wo hilney lagi, to phir usney pahad paida kiye aur unhen us (zameen ( par rakhney ka hukm farmaya to wo thehar gaee, farishton ko pahadon ki shiddat par tajjub hua to unhoney arz kya : rab ji ! kya teri makhluq mein pahadon se shadeed tar koi chiz hai? Allah Taala ne farmaya : haan , loha , to unhoney phir arz kya, rab ji ! kya teri makhluq mein lohey se bhi shadeed tar koi chiz hai? farmaya : haan , aag , unhoney arz kya, kya teri makhluq mein aag se bhi shadeed tar koi chiz hai? farmaya : haan , pani , unhoney arz kya : rab ji ! kya teri makhluq mein pani se shadeed tar koi chiz hai? farmaya : haan , hawa, phir unhoney arz kya : rab ji ! kya teri makhluq mein hawa se bhi shadeed tar koi chiz hai? farmaya : haan , wo ibne-Adam jo apney daain haath se sadqa karta hai to usey apney baaein hath se chhipa rakhta hai.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai, aur Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : ''sadqa khataeyn mita deta hai.'' kitabul-eman mein zikr ki gaee hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
1924,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo banda Muslim apney sarey maal se joda joda Allah ki raah mein kharch karta hai to jannat ke tamam darbaan apni apni nematon ke sath uska istaqbal kartey hain.'' maine arz kya, wo kaisey kharch karey ? farmaya : ''agar oont hon to do oont aur agar gaey hon to do gaey.'' rawahu Nasai ."
1925,"Hazrat Marsad bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke kisi sahabi ne mujhey hadees bayan ki ke usney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' roze-qiyamat momin ka sadqa hi uskey liye baaise-saya hoga .'' rawahu Ahmed ."
1926,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs aashoora ke din apney ehle w ayaal par faraakhi ke sath kharch karta hai to Allah pura saal usey faraakhi ata farma deta hai.'' Sufiyan ( Sauri (Raziallahu anhu)) ne farmaya : ham uska tajarba kar chukey hain, aur ham ne usey isi tarah paya hai. rawahu rizeen."
1927,"aur Imam Behaqi ne ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) , Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) , abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) aur Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se usey Shobil-emaan mein zikr kya hai, aur unhon (Imam Behaqi ( ne usey zaeef qarar diya hai."
1928,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya, Allah ke Nabi ! mujhey bataeyn ke sadqa ka kitna sawab hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ziyada se ziyada ( saat so guna (aur Allah ke yahan mazeed hai.''"
1929,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) aur Hakim bin Hizam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' behtareen sadqa wo hai jiskey peechey ghina ho aur sadqa ki ibtida (shuruat) apney zer kafalat afrad se kar .'' Bukhari , Muslim ne sirf Hakim (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki hai. muttafaq aleh."
1930,"Hazrat abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab musalman Allah ki raza aur husool sawab ki niyat se apney ehle w ayaal par kharch karta hai to wo uskey liye sadqa hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1931,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' eik Dinar wo hai jisey to ne Allah ki raah mein kharch kya, eik Dinar jo to ne gardan azad karney mein kharch kya eik Dinar wo hai jisey to ne kisi miskeen par kharch kya aur eik Dinar wo hai jisey to ne apney ehl w ayaal par kharch kya, un mein se sab se ziyada baaise-ajr wo hai jo to ne apney ehl w ayal par kharch kya. '' rawahu Muslim ."
1932,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' behtareen Dinar wo hai jisey aadmi apney ehl w ayaal par kharch karta hai aur wo Dinar hai jisey wo apney jihaadi ghodey par kharch karta hai aur wo Dinar hai jisey wo apney Mujahid sathiyon par kharch karta hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
1933,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! agar main abu-Salma ke beton par kharch karun to kya mujhey ajr milega jabkey wo merey bhi bete hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' un par kharch karo, tum un par jo kharch karogi to is par tumhen ajr w sawaab milega .'' muttafaq aleh."
1934,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki ehliya Zenab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' khawatin ki jamaat! sadqa karo, chaahey apney zewrat mein se karo.'' wo bayan karti hain mein (apney shohar) Abdullah ke paas wapis aai to maine kaha : aap gharib aadmi hain, jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen sadqa karney ka hukm farmaya hai, aap unke paas ja kar masla daryaft karen, agar to jayez ho to main tum par sadqa karun warna phir tumharey ilawa kisi aur par karun? wo bayan karti hain Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey farmaya : aap khud hi jaeyn, wo bayan karti hain, main gaee to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke darwazey par eik Ansari khatoon khadi thi usey bhi merey wala masla hi darpesh tha, wo bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) badi ba roab shakhsiyat they, pas Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey paas tashrif laye to ham ne unhen kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas jaao aur unhen bataao ke darwazey par do aurten aap se masla daryaft karti hain ke wo apna sadqa apney khaawindon aur unke zere-parwarish yateem bachon ko dey sakti hain? lekin unhen hamarey mutalliq na batana ke ham kon hain, Zenab kehti hain, Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur aap se masla puchha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se puchha ke wo dono kon hain? unhoney arz kya, eik Ansari khatoon aur eik Zenab hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kon si Zenab ?'' unhoney arz kya, Abdullah ki ehliya , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' un dono ke liye dugna ajr hai, qurbat daari ka ajr aur sadqey ka ajr .'' Bukhari , Muslim , alfaz hadees Muslim ke hain. muttafaq aleh."
1935,"Hazrat Memuna bint Haris (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur main eik londi azad ki, unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se uska zikr kya to aapney farmaya : ''agar tum usey apney mamuon ko dey deti to tumharey liye ziyada baais ajr hota .'' muttafaq aleh."
1936,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Allah ke Rasool ! merey do padosi hain, main un mein se kisey hadiya dun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' un mein se jiska darwaza tumharey ziyada qarib hai.'' Bukhari ."
1937,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum shorba banaao to is mein pani ziyada dala karo aur apney padosi ka bhi khayal rakha karo.'' rawahu Muslim ."
1938,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, unhoney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! kon sa sadqa afzal hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''gharib aadmi ka mehnat ki kamai se sadqa karna , aur apney zer kafalat afrad se aaghaz karna.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
1939,"Hazrat Salman bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' miskeen par sadqa karna sirf eik sadqa hai, jabkey rishte-daar par dohraa hai, sadqa aur sila rehmi.'' rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w Nasai w ibne-Maja w Darmi ."
1940,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney arz kya, merey paas eik Dinar hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey apni jaan par kharch kar.'' usney arz kya, merey paas eik aur hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey apney ehle w ayaal par kharch kar .'' usney arz kya, merey paas eik aur hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey apney khaadim par kharch kar .'' usney arz kya merey paas eik aur bhi hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''phir to behtar janta hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
1941,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya main tumhen behtareen shakhs ke barey mein na bataaun? Allah ki raah mein apney ghodey ki lagaam thaamney wala shakhs. kya main tumhen uskey qarib shakhs ke barey mein na bataaun? wo aadmi jo apni kuch bakriyan lekar alag thalak rehta hai, aur us barey mein Allah ka haq ada karta hai. kya main tumhen bad-tareen shakhs ke barey mein na bataaun ? wo aadmi jis se Allah ke naam par sawal kya jaey aur wo na dey .'' rawahu Tirmizi w Nasai w Darmi ."
1942,"Hazrat Umme-Bujaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' sawali ko kuch de-kar wapis kya karo chahey koi jali hui khuri ho.'' Malik , Nasai aur Imam Tirmizi aur Imam Abu-Dawood ne us maana mein riwayat kya hai."
1943,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs tum mein se Allah ke naam par panah talab karey to usey panah do , jo Allah ke naam par sawal karey to usey ata karo jo shakhs tumhen dawat dey to usey qubul karo, aur jis shakhs ne tumharey sath koi neki ki ho to tum usey badla do , agar tum badla chukaney ke liye kuch na paao to uskey liye is qadr dua karo ke tumhen yaqin ho jaey ke tum ne uska badla chuka diya hai.''"
1944,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki zaat ka wasta de-kar jannat ke siwa kuch na manga jaey.''"
1945,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ansaare-Madina mein khajuron ke lihaz se sab se ziyada maal daar they, aur unhen apney amwaal ( baghaat ( mein Biraha naami baagh sab se ziyada pasand tha, aur wo masjid ke samney tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wahan tashrif laya kartey aur wahan ka sheereen pani nosh farmaya kartey they, Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab ye aayat nazil hui : ''tum neki hasil nahin kar saktey jab tak apni pasandida chiz kharch na karo.'' to abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! Allah Taala farmata hai : ''tum neki hasil nahin kar saktey jab tak apni pasandida chiz kharch na karo.'' be-shak Birha baagh mujhey sab se ziyada pasand hai aur wo Allah Taala ke liye sadqa hai, main uskey sawab aur uskey Allah ke yahan zakhira honey ki ummid rakhta hun, Allah ke Rasool! Allah ke hukm ke mutabiq aap jaisey aur jahan chahen usey istimal karen, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bahut khub ! ye to bahut nafa bakhsh maal hai, aur tum ne jo kaha maine usey sun liya aur main to yehi chahta hun ke tum usey apney rishte daaron mein taqseem kar do.'' abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! main aisey hi karunga , abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey apney rishtey daaron aur apney chacha zaad bhaiyon mein taqseem kar diya. muttafaq aleh."
1946,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''behtareen sadqa ye hai ke to kisi bhookey pet ko sair kar dey.''"
1947,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab biwi israaf kiye baghair apney ghar ke khaney se sadqa karey to usey kharch karney ki wajeh sey, uskey shohar ko kamaaney ki wajeh se ajr milega aur khaazin ko bhi utna hi ajr milega aur koi kisi ke ajr mein kami nahin kerega .'' muttafaq aleh."
1948,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab aurat apney khawind ki kamai sey, uski ijazat ke baghair kharch karti hai to uskey liye uskey ajr se nisf milta hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1949,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' musalman ameen khaazin jo hukm ke mutabiq khush dili sey, jisey deney ko kaha jaey, mukammal taur par pura deta hai to wo bhi sadqa karney walon mein shumar hota hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1950,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke eik aadmi ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kya ke meri walida achcha faut ho gaeen, aur mera unke barey mein khayal hai ke agar wo baat kartin to sadqa kartin, to agar main unki taraf se sadqa kar dun to unhen ajr milega ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' haan .'' muttafaq aleh."
1951,"Hazrat abu Amaama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Hajjatil-wadaa ke khutbe mein farmatey huey suna : '' koi aurat apney khawind ki ijazat ke baghair uskey ghar se koi chiz kharch na karey.'' arz kya gaya, Allah ke Rasool ! khana bhi nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo to hamara behtareen maal hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
1952,"Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khawatin se baiat li to eik ba waqar ( buland qaamat ( khatoon khadi hui goya wo Muzar qabiley ki khatoon thi, usney arz kya, Allah ke Nabi ! ham apney baapon , beton aur shohron par bojh hain, so unke amwaal mein se hamarey liye kya halal hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tar-o-taza chizen jo tum khati ho aur hadiya karti ho.''"
1953,"Hazrat abi laham ke azad karda ghulam Umer bayan kartey hain, merey aaqa ne gosht bananey ke mutalliq mujhey hukm farmaya to itney main eik miskeen merey paas aaya maine is mein se kuch usey khila diya, merey aaqa ko uska pata chala to usney mujhey maara, main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur aap se ye waqia zikr kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey bula kar farmaya : ''tum ne usey kyon maara ?'' usney kaha : ye mera khana merey hukm ke baghair deta hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ajr tum dono ko milta hai.'' aur eik riwayat mein hai : unhoney kaha : main mamlook tha to maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla puchha : kya main apney malikon ke maal mein se koi chiz sadqa kar liya karun ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' haan , ajr tumharey darmiyan nisf nisf hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
1954,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine kisi shakhs ko fi sabeelillah eik ghoda bator sawari ata kya to usney usey zaya kar diya, maine usey kharidna chaha aur mujhey khayal hua ke wo usey maamuli qeemat par bech dega , maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla puchha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey kharido, na apna sadqa wapis lo chahey wo usey eik dirham main tumhen ata karey, kyonkey apna sadqa wapis leney wala kuttey ki tarah hai jo apni qai chaat jata hai.'' aur eik riwayat mein hai : '' apna sadqa wapis na ley , kyonkey apna sadqa wapis leney wala, apni qai chaatney waley ki tarah hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1955,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir tha jab eik khatoon aap ke paas aai , usney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! maine apni walida ko eik londi sadqa ki thi aur wo (yani walida ( wafat pa gaee hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tumhara ajr wajib ho gaya aur wo bator meeras tumharey paas wapis aa gaee .'' usney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! agar eik maah ke rozey uskey zimmey hon to kya main uski taraf se rozey rakhun ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' uski taraf se rozey rakho .'' us aurat ne arz kya : usney to Haj bhi nahin kya tha, to kya main uski taraf se Haj karun ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' haan , uski taraf se Haj karo.'' rawahu Muslim ."
